-file-height=\"570\" data-file-type=\"bitmap\" height=\"567\" width=\"1700\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></span></span>\n\t<span typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\" data-mw=\"{&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Delhi&quot;}\"><a href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Delhi\" title=\"Delhi\"><img alt=\"Delhi\" resource=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/File:DelhiBanner1.jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikivoyage/en/6/6b/DelhiBanner1.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" data-file-width=\"1710\" data-file-height=\"570\" data-file-type=\"bitmap\" height=\"567\" width=\"1700\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></p>\n</div>","link":"https://en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Previous_Destinations_of_the_month","retrieved":1761269123151},{"title":"Off the Beaten Path (Wikivoyage recommendations)","contents":"<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r4523569\" about=\"#mwt9\" typeof=\"mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion\" id=\"mwJg\" data-mw=\"{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;templatestyles&quot;,&quot;attrs&quot;:{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;Banner/styles.css&quot;},&quot;parts&quot;:[{&quot;template&quot;:{&quot;target&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;banner&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;./Template:Banner&quot;},&quot;params&quot;:{&quot;direction&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;right&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;Ko Kret&quot;},&quot;type&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;otbp&quot;},&quot;image&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;KoKretBanner1.jpg&quot;},&quot;quote&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;Experience the culture of the Mon people, including their pottery and cuisine, on this island just outside Bangkok.&quot;}},&quot;i&quot;:0}}]}\"><span about=\"#mwt9\">\n</span><div class=\"banner-image js-proportonal-resize notheme\" about=\"#mwt9\" id=\"mwJw\" style=\"font-size: 108%;\">\n\t<p><span class=\"mw-default-size nolink interactiveIcon\" typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\"><span><img resource=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/File:Interactive_icon.svg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e6/Int