<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Ko_Kret\" title=\"Ko Kret\">Experience the culture of the Mon people, including their pottery and cuisine, on this island just outside Bangkok.</a></div>\n\t</section></section></div>\n\t<p><span class=\"nolink\" typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\" data-mw=\"{&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Ko Kret&quot;}\"><span title=\"Ko Kret\"><img alt=\"Ko Kret\" resource=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/File:KoKretBanner1.jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikivoyage/en/6/6d/KoKretBanner1.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" data-file-width=\"1710\" data-file-height=\"570\" data-file-type=\"bitmap\" height=\"567\" width=\"1700\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></span></span>\n\t<span typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\" data-mw=\"{&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;Ko Kret&quot;}\"><a href=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Ko_Kret\" title=\"Ko Kret\"><img alt=\"Ko Kret\" resource=\"//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/File:KoKretBanner1.jpg\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikivoyage/en/6/6d/KoKretBanner1.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" data-file-width=\"1710\" data-file-height=\"570\" data-file-type=\"bitmap\" height=\"567\" width=\"1700\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></p>\n</div>","link":"https://en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Previously_Off_the_beaten_path","retrieved":1761269123153},{"title":"Featured Travel Topic (Wikivoyage recommendations)","contents":"<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r4523569\" about=\"#mwt11\" typeof=\"mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion\" id=\"mwKw\" data-mw=\"{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;templatestyles&quot;,&quot;attrs&quot;:{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;Banner/styles.css&quot;},&quot;parts&quot;:[{&quot;template&quot;:{&quot;target&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;banner&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;./Template:Banner&quot;},&quot;params&quot;:{&quot;direction&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;left&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;Broken Hill Xplorer&quot;},&quot;type&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;ftt&quot;},&quot;width&quot;:{&quot;wt&qu